snippet.title: Woodo - Official Trailer | ID@Xbox
snippet.description:
Get another look at the charming world of Woodo in this new trailer for the upcoming cozy 3D puzzle game. Learn more about the story and the start of your adventure, take a peek at puzzles, and more from this upcoming game that features diorama-style puzzle assembly mechanics. 

Woodo will be available on PC, Xbox Series X|S, PS5 (PlayStation 5), and Nintendo Switch.

#IGN #Gaming
